<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Prag</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen seiner Niederlassung in Prag den guten Leumund des Wenzel Schreiner und seiner Ehefrau Cristein mit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_127" id="63r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_127_r2l36">Der Altenſtat cʒu Prag / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_127_r2l37">Lieben frewnd / Als vventʒlaw <expan>Schrein<ex>er</ex></expan> / vnd Criſtein ſein elich <expan>wirt<ex>in</ex></expan> ſich nü furbas </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_127_r2l38">beÿ ew / vnd in <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat / mit <expan>demſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> hantvvergk cʒu begeen mainen / Sind für vns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_127_r2l39">etlich erberleute / vnd Meiſter <expan>desſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> hantvvergs / <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>Burg<ex>er</ex></expan> / den wır wol <expan>glaube<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_127_r2l40">haben vns geſagt beÿ Jren eiden / daʒ die <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> vventʒlaw / vnd <expan>Criſt<ex>ein</ex></expan> ſein elich <expan>wirt<ex>in</ex></expan> bede etvvÿ = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_127_r2l41">lang hie beÿ vns in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Stat gedienet / vnd ſich allcʒeit <expan>frümcklıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> haben / vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_127_r2l42">vns gebeten / daʒ vvir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>Erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> das alſo von Jren vvegen <expan>ſchreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllen <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sab<ex>a</ex>to</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_127_r2l43">vrbanj </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_127" id="63r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der Altenstat czu Prag </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieben frewnd, als Wenczlaw <expan>Schrein<ex>er</ex></expan> und Cristein,
                        sein elich <expan>wirt<ex>in</ex></expan>, sich nü furbas bey ew und in
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> stat mit
                            <expan>demselbe<ex>n</ex></expan> hantwergk czu begeen mainen, sind für
                        uns <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> etlich erber leute und meister
                                <expan>desselbe<ex>n</ex></expan> hantwergs,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>, den wir wol <expan>glaube<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        und haben uns gesagt bey iren eiden, daz die
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Wenczlaw und
                            <expan>Crist<ex>ein</ex></expan>, sein elich
                            <expan>wirt<ex>in</ex></expan>, bede etwylang hie bey uns in
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat gedienet und sich allczeit
                                <expan>frümcklich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> haben; und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        uns gebeten, daz wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> das also von iren wegen
                                <expan>schreib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllen.
                            <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>a</ex>to</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Urbani.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
</text>
